{"tid":1485320,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際戰線] 有Twitter嘅幫手like & retweet返818！！","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:00:40.000Z","uid":41818,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"09f32c2cf34ec0d05bdbb6555310720b97c8f7bb","tid":1485320,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>（818）（twitter召集）唔好再留係同溫層<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dGhJbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dGhJbS</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新戰術<br />\n去常見的tag#HongKongFreedom #HongKongers<br />\n#BoycottMulan<br />\n#Hongkongprotest #HongKongProtestors #Hongkongprotests #AntiELAB<br />\n<br />\n找出有哪些是外國人的post（例如：一些不是英文的文字、頭像是外國人&hellip;）<br />\n入去like，comment &quot;thank you for supporting us!&quot;，再加返今日818示威的和平相片，最後再follow對方。<br />\n<br />\n務求令到外國人（而不是自己的戰友，因為戰友不是文宣對象呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）對香港示威更加有興趣和關注<br />\n<br />\n人性啲咁諗，對方係幾千公里以外，睇post同我地速度都一樣，一分鐘10個post都說不定，呢個時候有條友走入去講句多謝，令佢覺得有face，有價值，咁佢都會再有下次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMyfOj3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMyfOj3.png&h=39f8732d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdHgxDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdHgxDL.png&h=8a1cf10c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da3eb7c8a8958454b9e77813e9aa757ffd985499","tid":1485320,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2c1719bb79110a107593b81e584c4e4fbc741b","tid":1485320,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"又話核彈都唔割？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484962\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484962</a>"},{"pid":"6aa0bf3a595d05f230b9e1c856b09f2f7353238a","ti