faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f010ae43aa895c062f1fd561153cf2bead83abd","tid":1485320,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2717602c467c5b24cfa4eb7492e9616decd155fe","tid":1485320,"uid":256966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"由7點玩twitter玩到而家00：40<br />\n唔係好知道實時的香港發生緊咩事<br />\n但係見到twitter的戰略性<br />\ntwitter用家唔會好care香港示威的細節，但係會被圖片／video去吸引，去share。<br />\n特別係名人 佢地講完香港之後就講返自己國家的野<br />\n<br />\n1）like、comment and upload有代表性的818遊行相片－－最好對返準佢講的話題去回覆，不過都比較多係：<br />\nThank you for your support!<br />\n(8.18_HK_Protest) 1.7 million people participate in a peaceful, reasonable, non-violent protest in Hong Kong today!<br />\nEven heavy rain cannot stop us!<br />\n再加hashtag<br />\n<br />\n2）retweet （有時可以不用with comment，因為我地個twitter account無外國人朋友，retweet都係俾自己友睇only）<br />\n<br />\n3）找到外國人的retweet，最好係外國名人，其次係外國普通twitter用家（follower人數唔會有幾十k），再去like、comment<br />\n<br />\n今日用得最多的4張相（因為twitter只可以4張圖片一個post）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89ZraZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89ZraZW.jpg&h=bb650ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ky5JXEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fky5JXEW.jpg&h=72720c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qNTArB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qNTArB.jpg&h=adc419d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRtC16C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRtC16C.jpg&h=11de0f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎去我個twitter @lam_chau_bar 去互follow，同埋睇下我的做法，找返那些多人like and comment的去做上述步驟<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知有幾大作用<br />\n但係，盡力做啦，又唔洗流血、唔流汗、又有冷氣和有得坐住用wifi，仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 